title: Nothing New (feat. Phoebe Bridgers) (Taylor's Version) (From The Vault)
description:
Taylor Swift and Phoebe Bridgers joined together for this beautiful song that hits you right in the gut as soon as you hear the lyrics. Taylor endured it all.. and Ana has a different take on some of the lyrics. How do you interpret them?
What did we miss? What would you like to hear from us? Let us know!
